mappings.name: Return the abuse ticket data for a given ticket id

schema.description: The associated fields returned, given a unique abuse ticket id

closedAt.description: The date the abuse ticket was closed

createdAt.description: The date the abuse ticket was created

domainIp.description: The domain or IP the suspected abuse was reported against

reporter.description: The shopper id of the person who reported the suspected abuse

source.description: The single URL or IP the suspected abuse was reported against

target.description: The company the suspected abuse is targeting

type.description: The type of abuse being reported
